<sentence>　歴史的仮名遣いで<event class="" eid="e137">書け</event>ば<quote>「歴史的仮名遣ひ」</quote>と<event class="" eid="e138">なる</event>。</sentence>
<sentence>例えば<quote>「私はお手植ゑの松の絵を<event class="" eid="e139">描かう</event>と<event class="" eid="e140">思つた</event>」</quote>のように、仮名遣いの基準を現代の発音に<event class="" eid="e141">よらず</event>、古文献に<event class="" eid="e142">おく</event>仮名遣いのこと。</sentence>
<sentence><TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" mod="START" tid="t22" type="DATE" value="PAST_REF" valueFromSurface="PAST_REF">江戸時代前期</TIMEX3>の国学者で歌人、契沖の整理に<event class="" eid="e143">従っ</event>て、基準を<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" mod="START" tid="t23" type="DATE" value="PAST_REF" valueFromSurface="PAST_REF">平安時代初期</TIMEX3>に<event class="" eid="e144">置く</event>。</sentence>
